285
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:59,400
We were worried that

286
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:01,039
he could not wake up before.

287
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,719
But he's awake now.

288
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,960
So, we should be more confident now.

289
00:14:05,719 --> 00:14:06,799
As long as he's not well,

290
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:08,400
