in the UK,

328
00:15:48,359 --> 00:15:49,159
I joined

329
00:15:49,239 --> 00:15:50,840
BlackRock in the UK.

330
00:15:51,119 --> 00:15:52,320
In those years,

331
00:15:52,559 --> 00:15:54,840
