334
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:02,880
What's the reason?

335
00:16:03,919 --> 00:16:05,799
Do you know
the Minsheng Road in Shanghai?

336
00:16:06,159 --> 00:16:07,039
I

337
00:16:07,559 --> 00:16:09,200
was the chief trader

338
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,479
