341
00:16:14,719 --> 00:16:15,719
I don't get it.

342
00:16:16,719 --> 00:16:17,880
I'm just like you.

343
00:16:18,039 --> 00:16:19,440
Didn't you take all
the responsibilities on your own?

344
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:21,280
How do you know that?

345
00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:22,840
Come out. It's time for exercise.

346
00:16:24,479 --> 00:16:26,479
