355
00:17:11,199 --> 00:17:11,760
Let's go.

356
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:43,599
Mr. Lei.

357
00:17:44,719 --> 00:17:45,520
Mr. Lei.

358
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,520
Guys.

359
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:49,680
Hello, uncle Duan.

