366
00:17:58,959 --> 00:17:59,920
He's awake.

367
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:01,680
Fine. I'll leave you alone.

368
00:18:01,719 --> 00:18:03,040
I'll make you some tea.

369
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:03,920
Go ahead.

370
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:09,119
Mr. Lei, I'm Lin Xiangyuan.

371
00:18:09,599 --> 00:18:10,719
Do you still remember?

372
00:18:17,800 --> 00:18:18,640
Mr. Lei,

373
00:18:18,839 --> 00:18:20,520
