399
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:31,280
Mr. Lin.

400
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:31,760
Back off!

401
00:19:31,839 --> 00:19:32,640
Let's go.

402
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,319
