416
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,640
It's fine. It's fine.

417
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,079
Yuzheng, they are all bad guys.

418
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,439
They're guests.

419
00:19:58,719 --> 00:19:59,880
You're bad, too.

420
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,719
Bad guy. Back off!

421
00:20:01,719 --> 00:20:02,199
Look!

422
00:20:02,199 --> 00:20:03,079
Back off! All of you!

423
00:20:03,439 --> 00:20:04,160
Good lord.

424
00:20:04,319 --> 00:20:05,839
He's yelling at everyone like this now?

425
00:20:06,479 --> 00:20:08,520
He's out of his mind sometimes.

426
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:10,760
Let's make it another day, shall we?

427
00:20:11,359 --> 00:20:12,199
Fine.

428
00:20:12,719 --> 00:20:13,479
Ask them to leave!

429
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,479
They 're gone.

430
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:16,920
Excuse me.

431
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:21,800
