433
00:20:29,239 --> 00:20:30,359
Got beaten for nothing.

434
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:31,680
He is out of your mind, isn't he?

435
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:33,400
Why is it so easy for him to get angry?

436
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:34,280
Never mind.

437
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,800
There is no need
to take offence at a patient.

438
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,199
Let him take it out.

439
00:20:38,719 --> 00:20:39,719
Just consider it as

440
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,160
an apology I make to him.

441
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:45,040
Now Lei Yuzheng is in jail.

442
00:20:45,599 --> 00:20:47,280
He is so sick.

443
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:51,479
Yutian shall count on me.

444
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:52,880
That's true.

445
00:20:53,079 --> 00:20:55,920
You're the manager
of Yutian from now on.

446
00:20:57,359 --> 00:21:00,079
